name: Other guarantee_Rank level - No detailed information available_Unsecured
description: A guarantee is provided by a non-government entity that would oblige the guarantor to make payments to the holder of the security if the issuer fails to meet the obligation to make repayments arising under the instrument secured by the guarantor.To be reported, in case the rank level (subordinated/senior/ABS) is not available / applicable. Securities are not backed by assets, future income streams or similar.
